ortunity to enhance their curriculum, and their career path, through programming and scholarship support.  We invite you to make a commitment today.   Please enter the amount of the contribution you wish to make below. You will then be directed to the University of Illinois Foundation’s secure Online Giving site for your personal and credit card information.  You can make a gift to any of the funds below:    Please note that if you do not wish to give online, you may:  MAIL YOUR CHECK:  Please make gifts by check or money order payable to the University of Illinois Foundation. Please also include a short note (or memo on your check) stating the purpose or designation of your gift. University of Illinois Foundation 1305 West Green Street, MC-386 Urbana, IL 61801      © Copyright 2014-2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois     Footer Navigation                    Vice Provost for Global Engagement  Office of External Scholarships  Office of Financial Aid  University Registrar  Centers for Diversity  Disability Resources  Privacy Policy  Contact Us     Translate »  Cookie Settings 